          passes):</p>
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_write-workflow.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;53:43">S-A, A-D, T-B, F-sentinel, B-M, sentinel-M, M-E</codeblock>
