          (rule 1) passes:</p>
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_write-workflow.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2;59:43">"steps": "S-1,1-D,T-6,F-1,6-M,1-M,M-E"</codeblock>
        </info>
